# 🧠 AI PDF Summariser

A full-stack web application that allows users to upload PDF documents and generate either **short**
or **detailed summaries** using Google's **Gemini API**. Built with **React**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **Flask**,
the app provides a fast and intuitive experience for summarizing long documents.
Summaries can be copied directly or downloaded as PDF files.

---

## ✨ Features

- 📄 Upload any `.pdf` document through the web interface
- 🤖 Generate **AI-based summaries** using Gemini API
- 🔀 Choose between **Short** or **Detailed summaries** using different system prompts
- 📋 Copy the generated summary to clipboard
- 📥 Download the summary as a `.pdf` file
- 💡 Clean and responsive UI built with React and Tailwind CSS

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

| Layer        | Technology                    |
|--------------|-------------------------------|
| Frontend     | React, Tailwind CSS           |
| Backend      | Flask (Python)                |
| AI Model     | Gemini API (Google GenAI)     |
| PDF Text Extraction | **PyMuPDF**       |
| Summary Export (PDF) | `html2pdf.js`   |

---
